---
// Solution.astro — What We Enable
---
<section class="section bg-radial-blue" id="product">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-label">✦ What We Enable</div>
      <h2>Satisfy compliance automatically<br/>so you can build.</h2>
      <p>We remove the friction between engineering and risk. Your agents don't change, but your governance posture is instantly upgraded.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Auto-scrolling carousel -->
  <div class="carousel-container">
    <div class="carousel-track">
      <!-- Group 1 -->
      <div class="carousel-items">
        <div class="carousel-card card">
          <div class="card-icon">🎬</div>
          <h3>Complete Visibility</h3>
          <p>Our system records everything. When compliance asks 'why?', you never have to scramble for details or reconstruct logs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-card card">
          <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Audit-Ready Evidence</h3>
          <p>We make all the details available in a format regulators understand, eliminating translation overhead between engineering and compliance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-card card">
          <div class="card-icon">🔒</div>
          <h3>Continuous Alignment</h3>
          <p>We work with legal experts to map rules directly into the platform, alerting you immediately if we see discrepancies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-card card">
          <div class="card-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>Deploy Your Way</h3>
          <p>We host in-house and on cloud, so you have the choice. Backed by 24x7 online support to guide you whenever you need us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Group 2 (Duplicate for seamless infinite scroll) -->
      <div class="carousel-items" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="carousel-card card">
          <div class="card-icon">🎬</div>
          <h3>Complete Visibility</h3>
          <p>Our system records everything. When compliance asks 'why?', you never have to scramble for details or reconstruct logs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-card card">
          <div class="card-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Audit-Ready Evidence</h3>
          <p>We make all the details available in a format regulators understand, eliminating translation overhead between engineering and compliance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-card card">
          <div class="card-icon">🔒</div>
          <h3>Continuous Alignment</h3>
          <p>We work with legal experts to map rules directly into the platform, alerting you immediately if we see discrepancies.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-card card">
          <div class="card-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>Deploy Your Way</h3>
          <p>We host in-house and on cloud, so you have the choice. Backed by 24x7 online support to guide you whenever you need us.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.carousel-container {
  width: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  padding: 2rem 0 4rem;
  position: relative;
}

/* Gradient fades on the edges */
.carousel-container::before,
.carousel-container::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 150px;
  z-index: 2;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.carousel-container::before {
  left: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--color-bg) 0%, transparent 100%);
}
.carousel-container::after {
  right: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(to left, var(--color-bg) 0%, transparent 100%);
}

.carousel-track {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2rem;
  width: max-content;
  animation: scroll 40s linear infinite;
}

.carousel-track:hover {
  animation-play-state: paused;
}

.carousel-items {
  display: flex;
  gap: 2rem;
}

.carousel-card {
  width: 350px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1rem;
  background: var(--color-surface);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  padding: 2rem;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  overflow: visible;
}

.carousel-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  border-color: var(--color-cyan);
}

.card-icon {
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  line-height: 1;
}

.carousel-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--color-text);
  margin: 0;
}

.carousel-card p {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--color-text-muted);
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin: 0;
}

@keyframes scroll {
  0% { transform: translateX(0); }
  100% { transform: translateX(calc(-50% - 1rem)); }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .carousel-card { width: 300px; padding: 1.5rem; }
  .carousel-container::before, .carousel-container::after { width: 60px; }
}
</style>
